| 5 | [05-java-core.md](05-java-core.md) | Java 8–17: OOP, collections, generics, streams, concurrency, memory model, exceptions |
| 6 | [06-spring-boot.md](06-spring-boot.md) | Spring & Spring Boot: IoC/DI, beans, REST, security/JWT, transactions, profiles, actuator |
| 7 | [07-databases-hibernate.md](07-databases-hibernate.md) | SQL, indexing, transactions/ACID, JPA/Hibernate, N+1, caching, migrations |
